01:06:29,986 --> 01:06:31,817
Will you leave Grovetown?

809
01:06:31,887 --> 01:06:34,981
I won't be returning after tonight.

810
01:06:37,226 --> 01:06:39,694
I want to come with you.

811
01:06:39,762 --> 01:06:42,287
Excuse me while I throw up.

812
01:06:45,434 --> 01:06:46,924
- Give it to me.
- You...

813
01:06:47,003 --> 01:06:48,766
Give me the fucking book.

814
01:06:50,940 --> 01:06:53,670
- Sadie, why are you...
- Shut the fuck up.

815
01:06:54,677 --> 01:06:55,666
You think I won't...

816
01:06:55,745 --> 01:06:57,303
Think I won't kill you for it?

817
01:06:57,380 --> 01:06:59,712
Think I won't kill some bitch for it?

818
01:07:01,283 --> 01:07:04,275
All right. Right here.

819
01:07:08,090 --> 01:07:10,581
Your brother died for this,

820
01:07:10,659 --> 01:07:11,887
you shit.

