01:07:17,099 --> 01:07:19,226
Sean was wrong.

822
01:07:19,301 --> 01:07:21,394
We all were.

823
01:07:21,470 --> 01:07:24,098
What happened to you?

824
01:07:25,908 --> 01:07:29,344
We decided on this
together, you and Sean.

825
01:07:31,447 --> 01:07:33,039
He gave his life.

826
01:07:33,115 --> 01:07:35,481
What's going on?

827
01:07:35,551 --> 01:07:37,815
The curse.

828
01:07:37,887 --> 01:07:40,583
He found it.

829
01:07:40,656 --> 01:07:43,386
It was his idea, honey.

830
01:07:47,463 --> 01:07:50,455
