in your pretty little town to die,

831
01:07:50,533 --> 01:07:52,023
you included.

832
01:07:54,703 --> 01:07:56,796
This is true?

833
01:07:56,872 --> 01:08:00,103
Seems you two have a lot to talk about.

834
01:08:00,176 --> 01:08:03,634
It was a mistake.

835
01:08:03,712 --> 01:08:06,180
Sorry, choir girl.

836
01:08:06,248 --> 01:08:09,149
Burning times are back.

837
01:08:09,218 --> 01:08:10,947
Except this time...

838
01:08:12,455 --> 01:08:14,719
it's for the rest of the fucking world.

839
01:08:17,493 --> 01:08:18,824
Come on.

840
01:08:18,894 --> 01:08:20,486
Why would I go anywhere with you?

841
01:08:20,563 --> 01:08:23,225
- Lindsay...
- You lied to me.

842
01:08:23,299 --> 01:08:24,664
We don't have time for this right now.

843
01:08:24,733 --> 01:08:26,530
You're killing people.

844
01:08:26,602 --> 01:08:29,901
Sadie will destroy the book
if we don't stop her. And then...

845
01:08:31,373 --> 01:08:33,807
And then you will die.

846
01:08:53,796 --> 01:08:55,229
Paul, you grab the front.

847
01:08:55,297 --> 01:08:56,423
Hey, Lindsay might be inside.

848
01:08:56,499 --> 01:08:57,523
- Yeah, so?
- So be careful.

849
01:09:00,336 --> 01:09:02,201
Lindsay!

850
01:09:02,271 --> 01:09:04,671
- Lindsay!
- No!

851
01:09:08,077 --> 01:09:09,442
Sean died for nothing.

852
01:09:13,749 --> 01:09:15,341
Go!

853
01:09:15,417 --> 01:09:17,749
Aidan!

854
01:09:19,688 --> 01:09:21,383
Knock-knock!

855
01:09:21,457 --> 01:09:23,823
We want to talk to you, Aidan.

856
01:09:23,893 --> 01:09:25,019
Lindsay?

857
01:09:25,094 --> 01:09:27,585
We're here.

858
01:09:27,663 --> 01:09:29,654
Come out now. We won't hurt you.

859
01:09:29,732 --> 01:09:31,290
No we won't.

860
01:09:31,367 --> 01:09:32,459
Upstairs.

861
01:09:40,943 --> 01:09:43,207
There's nobody down here.

862
01:09:56,625 --> 01:09:58,354
Oh, fuck!

863
01:09:58,427 --> 01:10:00,622
- We got her!
- Shit.

864
01:10:00,696 --> 01:10:02,459
Fuck!

865
01:10:03,399 --> 01:10:05,629
No.

866
01:10:08,737 --> 01:10:10,295
Where's Aidan?

867
01:10:12,508 --> 01:10:14,373
No, no, no. No, go back.

868
01:10:18,247 --> 01:10:20,147
Oh, shit. That hurt, huh?

869
01:10:22,585 --> 01:10:24,815
Can't you do it here?

870
01:10:24,887 --> 01:10:26,354
No.

871
01:10:26,422 --> 01:10:28,322
I need time.

872
01:10:28,390 --> 01:10:30,381
Your worthless god can kiss my ass.

873
01:10:30,459 --> 01:10:31,756
What was that?

874
01:10:34,463 --> 01:10:37,159
Hey, stay here. Take care of the bitch.

875
01:10:37,233 --> 01:10:39,098
Fine. I'll take care of her.

876
01:10:50,079 --> 01:10:52,775
Paul, to the woods!

877
01:11:09,765 --> 01:11:11,699
Lindsay!

878
01:11:17,906 --> 01:11:20,875
The devil must be strong in you.

879
01:11:23,212 --> 01:11:25,180
The mother went much easier.

880
01:11:36,992 --> 01:11:42,020
It was in prison
that the Lord came to me.

881
01:11:42,097 --> 01:11:44,725
Then he gave me a purpose.

882
01:11:44,800 --> 01:11:47,394
One night, after a...

883
01:11:48,404 --> 01:11:49,598
particularly painful day,

884
01:11:49,672 --> 01:11:51,196
he spoke to me.

885
01:11:53,976 --> 01:11:55,705
And he said to me, "Hey, Roy?"

886
01:11:59,114 --> 01:12:00,979
Then, I said, "Yeah, God?"

887
01:12:03,652 --> 01:12:05,586
He said, "I want you to be a soldier.

888
01:12:05,654 --> 01:12:09,090
"I want you to be a soldier of the Lord."

889
01:12:12,961 --> 01:12:16,795
"And anytime there's
a soul that's lost or..."

890
01:12:18,434 --> 01:12:20,994
"possessed or

891
01:12:21,070 --> 01:12:23,129
beyond hope..."

892
01:12:29,278 --> 01:12:32,042
"I want you to send that soul
straight to hell."

893
01:12:40,055 --> 01:12:42,046
Now, are you gonna pray with me?

894
01:12:45,060 --> 01:12:46,823
No.

895
01:12:49,932 --> 01:12:52,765
Well, then I'm gonna
need you to shut the fuck up.

896
01:13:02,644 --> 01:13:05,010
Lindsay!

897
01:13:15,491 --> 01:13:16,651
I gotta draw 'em away.

898
01:13:16,725 --> 01:13:18,556
Meet me by the pier.

899
01:13:44,686 --> 01:13:47,484
Look, I just want you to understand

900
01:13:47,556 --> 01:13:50,616
my work here tonight

901
01:13:50,692 --> 01:13:53,627
is God's work.

902
01:13:53,695 --> 01:13:55,526
I am an instrument...

903
01:13:57,433 --> 01:13:58,491
...of his will.

904
01:14:04,740 --> 01:14:06,640
My hands...

905
01:14:08,744 --> 01:14:09,802
...are his.

906
01:14:09,878 --> 01:14:11,140
No, no. No, no, no.

907
01:14:12,714 --> 01:14:14,306
I know.

908
01:15:29,124 --> 01:15:32,616
Our Father, Who art in Heaven,

909
01:15:32,694 --> 01:15:34,457
Hallowed be Thy name...

910
01:15:51,113 --> 01:15:52,740
It wasn't my book.

911
01:16:05,060 --> 01:16:06,527
Aidan!

912
01:16:17,973 --> 01:16:19,907
Aidan!

913
01:16:19,975 --> 01:16:22,535
Thy pain is thy cleansing.

914
01:18:20,762 --> 01:18:22,389
Lindsay?

915
01:18:24,900 --> 01:18:26,060
Lindsay!

916
01:18:27,436 --> 01:18:29,461
Stop. Stop!

917
01:18:30,906 --> 01:18:32,533
Stop. Stop, hey...

918
01:18:32,607 --> 01:18:36,634
Stop. Look at me. Look at me.

919
01:18:36,712 --> 01:18:38,612
It's me.

920
01:18:45,854 --> 01:18:47,446
How long will it take?

921
01:18:47,522 --> 01:18:48,819
Not long.

922
01:19:26,294 --> 01:19:27,852
Is it over?

923
01:19:32,134 --> 01:19:33,931
You remember when I told you

924
01:19:34,002 --> 01:19:35,867
certain spells...

925
01:19:37,439 --> 01:19:39,339
require a terrible price?

926
01:19:44,813 --> 01:19:46,713
What I need to do...

927
01:19:48,583 --> 01:19:50,380
You have to understand,

928
01:19:50,452 --> 01:19:54,548
Sean gave his life to start the curse.

929
01:19:54,623 --> 01:19:56,682
What are you saying?

930
01:19:58,593 --> 01:20:00,891
Sacrifice started it.

931
01:20:02,864 --> 01:20:04,889
And sacrifice needs to end it.

932
01:20:19,581 --> 01:20:21,572
It's the only way.

933
01:20:21,650 --> 01:20:23,709
No.

934
01:20:23,785 --> 01:20:26,276
No, it can't be.

935
01:20:29,658 --> 01:20:32,092
No, Aidan. Please, no.

936
01:20:34,262 --> 01:20:36,958
You have to destroy
the book after it's done.

937
01:20:37,032 --> 01:20:38,124
Listen to me.

938
01:20:38,200 --> 01:20:40,327
You have to make sure

939
01:20:40,402 --> 01:20:42,393
