01:24:04,939 --> 01:24:07,271
This wasn't a suicide.

962
01:24:09,778 --> 01:24:11,473
Lindsay said he shot himself.

963
01:24:11,546 --> 01:24:14,276
Well, she was wrong.

964
01:24:16,251 --> 01:24:19,220
